      <hedline>
        <hl1>Interior Dept. Distorted Plan for Fire Island Dumes</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Fire Island Assn first vice president Bob Spencer letter on June 18 article holds Army Corps of Engineers' interim beach replenishment plan was not undertaken properly (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Re: ''Army Corps May Give Up Fire Island Plan'' [June 18]:</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Re: ''Army Corps May Give Up Fire Island Plan'' [June 18]:</p>
        <p>The Corps's ''interim plan'' to rebuild beaches and dunes with dredged sand was to have filled the entirety of Fire Island, but the Department of Interior allowed the plan to place sand only in front of Fire Island communities and the lighthouse so that it would appear to be a ''homeowner-selfish'' plan.</p>
        <p>BOB SPENCER  First Vice President  Fire Island Association</p>
      </block>
    </body.content>
